1.Provide properties in external file app.properties/app.yml
2.Provide properties when executing a jar:
    java -jar movie-catalog-service-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar --my.greeting="Hello world from Command line argument"
3.System properties - also accessible through @Value
4. profiles: set when executiog jar with vm option -Dspring.profiles.active=test
    java -jar movie-catalog-service-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar -Dspring.profiles.active=test